Date: Thu, 11 Jun 2026 12:03:30 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 1/3] ADD reviewed-feature closure prompt so accepted patch
 chats can be closed or reopened

After a clean review, the controller asks the patch-agent session for a local yes/no decision. Confirming closes the chat without sending the confirmation to the backend, while later user text reopens the session and continues the feature.
