+When review finishes without findings for a user-agent patch, the controller appends a
+`work-leaf: is this feature done? yes/no` prompt to that patch-agent session. A `yes` or `y` reply
+answers the prompt locally, appends `work-leaf: feature closed`, and does not send that confirmation
